  "_README": "Importable OBS Studio scene collection for the Gamified control deck. File > Scene Collection > Import in OBS and pick this file. Before going live: (1) find-and-replace YOUR_APP_URL with your Fly.io hostname e.g. gamified.fly.dev, (2) find-and-replace YOUR_ROOM with your VDO Ninja room name, (3) find-and-replace the 7 VIEW_CONTESTANT_* tokens with the push tokens each contestant is broadcasting. See README.md for the VDO Ninja director/guest setup. Canvas is 1920x1080; slot coords come straight from src/slots.ts percentages so the backdrop and the overlay's cutouts line up. Layers, bottom-up: backdrop image, 7 VDO Ninja browser sources at slot positions, transparent UI overlay on top. Flip to Pattern A (backdrop baked into overlay, no separate backdrop layer) by deleting the 'Backdrop' item and removing ?transparent=1 from the Overlay source URL.",
